    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>That is the best way to check it. You could write a helper method to do it:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static boolean isNullOrEmpty( final Collection&lt; ? &gt; c ) {\n    return c == null || c.isEmpty();\n}\n\npublic static boolean isNullOrEmpty( final Map&lt; ?, ? &gt; m ) {\n    return m == null || m.isEmpty();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
