    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you use Spring frameworks, then you can use <code>CollectionUtils</code> to check against both Collections (List, Array) and Map etc.</p>\n\n<pre><code>if(CollectionUtils.isEmpty(...)) {...}\n</code></pre>\n"
