    "question_id" : 12721076,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>org.apache.commons.lang.Validate</code>'s \"<a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/javadocs/api-3.1/org/apache/commons/lang3/Validate.html#notEmpty(T)\" rel=\"noreferrer\">notEmpty</a>\" method:</p>\n\n<p><code>Validate.notEmpty(myCollection)</code> -> Validate that the specified argument collection is neither null nor a size of zero (no elements); otherwise throwing an exception.</p>\n"
  }, {
