    "answer_id" : 78598335,
    "question_id" : 12721076,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As an extension to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/12722291/3679900\">@Jalayn's answer</a>, if your'e using AWS SDK, you can also use <a href=\"https://sdk.amazonaws.com/java/api/latest/software/amazon/awssdk/utils/CollectionUtils.html#isNullOrEmpty(java.util.Collection)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>CollectionUtils.isNullOrEmpty(..)</code></a></p>\n<p>References</p>\n<ol>\n<li>GitHub: <a href=\"https://github.com/aws/aws-sdk-java/blob/master/aws-java-sdk-core/src/main/java/com/amazonaws/util/CollectionUtils.java#L23\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>CollectionUtils.java</code></a></li>\n<li>AWS SDK docs: <a href=\"https://sdk.amazonaws.com/java/api/latest/software/amazon/awssdk/utils/CollectionUtils.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>CollectionUtils</code></a></li>\n</ol>\n"
